Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.13,0:23:00.53,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}笑いながら歌を歌おう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.53,0:23:04.09,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}胸に秘めた涙を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.19,0:23:07.94,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}交わすグラスに溶かして
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.94,0:23:10.83,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}出会えた人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.02,0:23:12.75,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}別れた夢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.09,0:23:16.99,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}掛け値のない人生よ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.99,0:23:20.98,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}愛を纏って歌うのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.98,0:23:24.63,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}乾杯をしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.13,0:23:30.71,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}冒険の日々に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.95,0:22:21.25,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}在黃昏的街道上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.45,0:22:26.17,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}長長的身影持續愈伸愈長
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.44,0:22:29.87,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}彷彿能聽見遠方傳來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.87,0:22:33.47,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}呼喚著某人的聲響
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.59,0:22:38.39,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}讓人喘不過氣的重擔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.39,0:22:42.98,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}通通消失的魔幻時光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.49,0:22:47.16,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}如同奇蹟般的 又隨處可見的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.16,0:22:50.16,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}夜晚就此開幕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.38,0:22:51.71,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}讓我們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.95,0:22:55.72,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}雙手打著拍子 此起彼落地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.13,0:23:00.53,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}邊開懷大笑邊放聲高歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.53,0:23:04.09,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}連藏在心中的眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.19,0:23:07.94,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}也溶入了傳來傳去的酒杯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.94,0:23:10.83,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}無論邂逅的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.02,0:23:12.75,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}或是訣別的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.09,0:23:16.99,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}都是這再真實不過的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.99,0:23:20.98,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}置身這片愛中 引吭高歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.98,0:23:24.63,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}盡情乾杯吧
